    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Available is a meticulously maintained 981-generation Porsche Cayman, featuring the sought-after 2.7L naturally aspirated flat-six power plant. This mid-engine masterpiece offers exceptional rotational inertia and optimal weight distribution. The 6-speed manual transaxle provides crisp, short-throw engagement, while the chassis utilizes a lightweight aluminum-steel composite construction to ensure high torsional rigidity. The suspension maintains its factory-spec damping rates, and the electromechanical steering delivers precise feedback through the apex. Recent preventative maintenance includes a full cooling system pressure test and a comprehensive brake bleed. This is a mechanically sound, driver-focused machine that balances visceral performance with daily usability.",
